                Late Pick-Ups
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                If your pet is not picked up within 30 minutes of your assigned pick-up time, a late fee of $5 will be applied for every 15 minutes thereafter. If your pet is not picked up by the salon's closing time for the day, you will be charged an $85.00 kennel fee. You agree to pay any applicable late pick-up fees as outlined.
              </p>
            </section>

