            <section class="mb-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green/10 to-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-green font-bold text-sm">8</span>
                Late Drop-Offs
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                If you arrive 30 minutes or more late for your scheduled drop-off time, we may either charge a late fee or be unable to accommodate your appointment. You agree to adhere to your scheduled drop-off time and to pay any applicable late fees if assessed.
              </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 9 -->
            <section class="mb-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green/10 to-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-green font-bold text-sm">9</span>
                No-Shows & Cancellations
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                No-shows and last-minute cancellations are subject to a fee of 50% of the full service fee per pet. If you cancel within 48 hours of your appointment, you will be charged this fee. We understand that emergency situations may arise, and we will work with you on a case-by-case basis, but repeated cancellations or no-shows will not be accommodated. As a by-appointment business, we rely on timely cancellations to offer slots to other clients. Cancellations must be made by calling or texting through MoeGo; we do not accept cancellations via email. You agree to adhere to our cancellation policy and pay any applicable fees for no-shows or late cancellations.
