              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Lillian Ruff Pet Spa operates as a by-appointment business, and our schedules are created based on the specific details provided for each pet, including breed, weight, and the type of service requested.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
