                These Terms, along with any policies referenced herein, constitute the entire agreement between you and Lillian Ruff Pet Spa regarding our grooming services, superseding any prior agreements or understandings, whether oral or written. Any ambiguities in the interpretation of these Terms shall not be construed against the drafting party.
              </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 17 -->
            <section class="mb-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green/10 to-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-green font-bold text-sm">17</span>
